article_title: Utah Gov Gary Herbert's Obamacare Expansion Won't Work -- And Neither Will Its Enrollees

og.description: Utah is often seen as a national leader for its values of helping individuals help themselves. Yet, the Obamacare Medicaid expansion undermines that very value system.
